<H1><IMG SRC="glomop.gif" NATURALSIZEFLAG="3" HEIGHT=50 WIDTH=50 ALIGN=BOTTOM><I>GloMop</I>:
Global Mobile Computing by Proxy</H1>

<UL>
<LI><B><I>No computer is an island.</I></B> 

<LI><B><I>Never put off for tomorrow's hardware what you can do with today's
software.</I></B> 
</UL>


