<LI>Chon-chon Tang (undergraduate)</LI>
d191 14
a204 6
<DD>This <A HREF="http://HTTP.CS.Berkeley.EDU/~fox/glomop/pythia.html">publicly
accessible</A> HTTP proxy shows how <A HREF="http://HTTP.CS.Berkeley.EDU/~fox/glomop/overview.html#distillation">distillation</A>
can be exploited for bandwidth management while surfing the Web using a
slow (e.g. 28.8K) connection. Pythia distills GIF, JPEG, and PostScript,
and can also strip Java tags and background GIFs and a few other nifty
things. </DD>
